            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1674577963090-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir <strong>half </strong>the <strong>cultured coconut </strong>into the <strong>dal</strong> with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and serve in bowls</p><p>Serve the <strong>vegetable samosas</strong> to the side with the <strong>coriander chutney</strong>, <strong>tamarind sauce </strong>and <strong>remaining cultured coconut</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
